OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWednesday morning will be dry
OL,6,Fand bright, with some sunny spells
OL,7,Flikely. Increasing cloud might bring
OL,8,Fsome light rain late in the day with a
OL,9,Ffreshening wind. Feeling warm by
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAn increasingly cloudy
OL,13,Fevening and night with some rain
OL,14,Faffecting the region. Some heavier
OL,15,Fbursts are likely across the
OL,16,FDerbyshire Hills. Drier later in the
OL,17,Fnight. Gusty winds for most.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
