OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAny early showers or rain
OL,6,Fclearing early Thursday morning, then
OL,7,Fdry and breezy, with some clear or
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Temperatures close to
OL,9,Faverage.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday
OL,12,Fand into the weekend likely to remain
OL,13,Fdry and breezy, with some clear or
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Temperatures close to or
OL,15,Fa little above average throughout.
